TextEng: I'll make it worth your while to let me in.
Text: 들여보내 주면 그 수고에 보답을 해 주지.

TextEng: What if I join a group you let in?
Text: 네가 들여보낸 단체에 내가 가입하면 어때?

TextEng: How about five Smugglers' Coins. Not too shabby.
I've a few Smugglers' Coins, the currency of the black market.
Text: 밀수업자의 주화가 몇 개 있어요. 암시장의 화폐죠.

TextEng: My dear lady, I'm sure we can come to some... agreement.
Text: 아가씨, 우리... 어떤 합의에 이를 수 있겠죠.

TextEng: My services, in any way you see fit to use them.
Text: 제 봉사를, 어떤 방식으로든 사용하실 수 있어요.

TextEng: I can offer gold.
Let me in! Aribeth decreed I must keep the peace!
Is this a black market tavern?
How can I join one of these groups if you don't let me in?
Text: 들여보내지 않으면 어떻게 이 단체에 가입하겠어?

TextEng: Who do I have to be to get in?
What me have to do to get in?
This black market tavern?
You let me in! Me keep the peace!
Me make it worth your while.
How me join if you not let me in?
Me give gold?
Maybe me work for yous?
Well, me pretty studly. Maybe we make... agreement?
Text: 흠, 나 꽤 멋지다. 우리... 합의 볼래?

TextEng: Me have some Smugglers' Coins.
Me got five Smugglers' Coins. That good?
Me not have much. How me join group?
Text: 나 가진 거 많지 않아. 어떻게 무리 들어가?
